FT  02 SEP 92 / UK Company News: Losses at Arcon Intl deepen to IPounds
367,000
Losses at Arcon International Resources, formerly known as Conroy Petroleum
and Natural Resources, rose from IPounds 145,000 to IPounds 367,000 (Pounds
348,000) pre-tax for the six months to February 29.
Turnover totalled IPounds 348,000 (IPounds 15,000). Losses per share worked
through at 0.0087p (0.0034p).
